summary: I was really bored with the lack of stuff in the Breezehome so I did a slight remodel on it!
descriptionHtml: Before you go too far into my mod, please be aware that I am huge Doctor Who fan, so like the Tardis, my house is bigger on the inside than on the outside...or small on the outside than on the inside (if you saw the Christmas Episode)!  So the house consists of everything you need to play the game including a Enchantment Table, Alchemy Table, Workbench, Smelter, Grindstone, Anvil (no forge as they take up too much space), and if you notice the extra stuff is closed off.  Other than that I added a better bed and some other things.  I hope you enjoy it as it is my first REAL mod.  I have modded other player houses as well, but I am in the process of testing them for bugs, so enjoy my first one!
author: akparky
